# Physics Simulation

## vector and d3 based bouncing ball

### Sections
   * #### Vector
      * provides basic vector functions
   * #### Collider
      * check for collisions
 
   * #### mover
      * moves in responds to vector forces 
      * updates velocity 
      * checks basic collisions
      * displays itself
   * #### SystemController
      * controls system of movers
